response.original_title: NJPW Road To Tokyo Dome 2018 - Day 1
response.overview: On December 17, 2017, NJPW's Road to Tokyo Dome tour kicked off at Korakuen Hall in Tokyo, broadcast on TV Asahi. The main event featured a NEVER Openweight Six Man Tag Team Title Match between BULLET CLUB and Los Ingobernables de Japon. Another notable match had CHAOS' Kazuchika Okada and YOSHI-HASHI facing Los Ingobernables de Japon's Hiromu Takahashi and Tetsuya Naito in a tag team bout. Other wrestlers on the show include Kota Ibushi, Tiger Mask, and Suzuki-gun, among more!
response.title: NJPW Road To Tokyo Dome 2018 - Day 1
